snippet.title: Champion Unmasked: Nightmare Robin
snippet.description:
Slice through evil as Nightmare Robin, the scourge of vampires. He joins Infinite Crisis, the DC MOBA, as a lightning-quick Assassin trained by the likes of Batman and Talia al Ghul.

Do you want to stalk the night as Damien Wayne? Sign up and play Infinite Crisis for FREE at http://www.infinitecrisis.com!
